{"type":"markdown","aggs":[],"params":{"fontSize":12,"openLinksInNewTab":false,"markdown":"# Zeek SMB Dashboard

### *Dashboard Details*

Without additional queries or filters, this dashboard provides an overall summary of Zeek SMB related logs for the time frame selected. This includes both SMB Mapping and SMB Files logs.

Panels that are pinned to a specific log are indicated via square brackets, description, or title. Ex. [SMB Mappings]
Otherwise the results are included for both SMB Mappings and SMB Files.

Pinning certain fields will cause certain panels to return no results because those fields don't exist in the other log type.

Pinning specific UIDs and IP addresses provides the best summary of SMB related activity.

Pivot to other dashboards by pinning your filters and using the dashboard links navigation above.
"},"title":"Zeek-SMB_MAPPING-Header"}
